{
  "id": "nce4-l5",
  "title": "Lesson 5: Youth",
  "audio": "/audio/nce4/05ÔºçYouth.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 5",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.31,
      "endTime": 2.27
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Youth",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.28,
      "endTime": 9.32
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How does the writer like to treat young people?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.33,
      "endTime": 14.43
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "People are always talking about 'the problem of youth'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.44,
      "endTime": 20.17
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "If there is one -- which I take leave to doubt",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.18,
      "endTime": 24.25
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "-- then it is older people who create it, not the young themselves.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 24.26,
      "endTime": 29.97
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Let us get down to fundamentals and agree that the young are after all human beings",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.98,
      "endTime": 36.73
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "-- people just like their elders.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.74,
      "endTime": 39.59
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "There is only one difference between an old man and a young one:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "endTime": 44.99
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the young man has a glorious future before him",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45,
      "endTime": 48.84
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and the old one has a splendid future behind him: and maybe that is where the rub is.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 48.85,
      "endTime": 57.11
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When I was a teenager, I felt that I was just young and uncertain --",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.12,
      "endTime": 63.41
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "that I was a new boy in a huge school,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 63.42,
      "endTime": 66.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and I would have been very pleased to be regarded as something so interesting as a problem.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.66,
      "endTime": 73.56
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "For one thing, being a problem gives you a certain identity,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.57,
      "endTime": 78.91
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and that is one of the things the young are busily engaged in seeking.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 78.92,
      "endTime": 84.13
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I find young people exciting.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 84.14,
      "endTime": 87.08
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They have an air of freedom,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 87.09,
      "endTime": 89.41
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and they have not a dreary commitment to mean ambitions or love of comfort.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.42,
      "endTime": 95.46
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They are not anxious social climbers, and they have no devotion to material things.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.47,
      "endTime": 102.96
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "All this seems to me to link them with life and the origins of things.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 102.97,
      "endTime": 109.62
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It's as if they were in some sense cosmic beings in violent and lovely contrast with us suburban creatures.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 109.63,
      "endTime": 119.56
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "All that is in my mind when I meet a young person.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 119.57,
      "endTime": 124.35
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He may be conceited, ill-mannered,  presumptuous or fatuous,  but I do not turn for protection to dreary cliches about respect for elders --",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 124.36,
      "endTime": 136.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "as if mere age were a reason for respect.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 136.79,
      "endTime": 141.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I accept that we are equals, and I will argue with him, as an equal, if I think he is wrong.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 141.38,
      "endTime": 146.38
    }
  ]
}